*sylpheed-0.8.6 (25 Nov 2002)

  26 Nov 2002; Spider <spider@gentoo.org> sylpheed-0.8.6.ebuild : I updated
  the ebuild so It actually adheres to USE flags now.  missed a ${myconf} in a critical place.

  25 Nov 2002; Brad Cowan <bcowan@gentoo.org> sylpheed-0.8.6.ebuild,
  files/digest-sylpheed-0.8.6:
  
  Version bump. Totally redid ebuild to work with USE vars, then realized
  leonardop already did basically the same thing in an -r1 version.

*sylpheed-0.8.5-r1 (16 Nov 2002)

  16 Nov 2002; L. Boshell <leonardop@gentoo.org> : Use econf and einstall.
  Implement the `ipv6' USE var. Install .desktop and .png files when the
  `gnome' USE var is present.

